title: Werewolf Rising 2014 1080p BluRay
description:
===================================================================================
Emma is a country girl who left for the big city only to return years later with big problems. And when she returns to her childhood home deep in the Arkansas
mountains for some well needed rest| relaxation| and soul searching| her problems have only just begun. A bloodthirsty werewolf emerges from the woods to lay siege
to the area| ravaging anything in its path and revealing a sinister underworld that most never knew existed. With a full moon hanging over the area| Emma is plunged
into a fight not only for her life| but for her very soul...
